der.com%2Fi-spent-one-month-getting-rejected-daily-what-i-learned-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehumiliated%20by%20the%20rejection%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20reluctant%20to%20return%20to%20the%20post%20office.%20Eventually%2C%20though%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20act%20like%20an%20adult%20and%20go%20retrieve%20my%20mail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20my%20relief%2C%20one%20of%20the%20other%20guys%20was%20working%20the%20counter%2C%20and%20I%20handed%20him%20my%20yellow%20package%20slip.%20Uriah%20suddenly%20emerged%20from%20the%20back%20office%2C%20made%20a%20beeline%20for%20the%20counter%2C%20and%20took%20the%20slip%20out%20of%20his%20colleague's%20hand.%20Our%20eyes%20met%2C%20and%20when%20he%20brought%20my%20packages%20back%2C%20he%20shyly%20told%20me%20he'd%20call%20me.%20Apparently%2C%20he%20hadn't%20known%20who%20I%20was%20until%20that%20day.%20He%20called%20that%20night.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db0cbe0d-a4e9-4a42-8055-5828800cbd61%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20told%20a%20stranger%20on%20a%20ferry%20he%20was%20going%20to%20make%20me%20his%20wife%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20first%20date%20was%20going%20to%20Ke'e%20Beach%20to%20watch%20the%20sunset%2C%20and%20things%20moved%20quickly%20after.%20It%20was%20April%2C%20and%20I%20was%20leaving%20at%20the%20end%20of%20May%20to%20spend%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-know-before-spending-six-months-in-europe-mistakes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esix%20weeks%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20opened%20the%20exclusivity%20discussion%20when%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20my%20upcoming%20trip%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20see%20other%20people%2C%20but%20I%20understood%20if%20he%20did.%20He%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BJulia%2C%20not%20only%20do%20I%20not%20want%20to%20see%20other%20people%20while%20you're%20in%20Europe%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20want%20to%20see%20other%20people%20again%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20about%20a%20month%20after%20our%20first%20date%2C%20and%20while%20his%20words%20filled%20me%20with%20happiness%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20explain%20that%20while%20I%20would%20love%20to%20spend%20my%20life%20with%20him%2C%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fovercoming-fear-of-commitment-pregnancy-marriage-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edidn't%20want%20to%20get%20married%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20I%20never%20had.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20never%20wanted%20to%20get%20married%20before%20either%2C%20but%20now%20he%20had%20changed%20his%20mind.%20As%20calm%20and%20kind%20as%20ever%2C%20he%20said%20he%20knew%20I%20would%20come%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20leaving%20Hawai'i%20for%20Europe%2C%20he%20flew%20with%20me%20to%20New%20England%20to%20meet%20my%20family.%20After%20a%20few%20drinks%20at%20The%20Oar%20and%20Yellow%20Kittens%20on%20Block%20Island%2C%20on%20the%20ferry%20home%2C%20I%20heard%20him%20tell%20some%20guys%20he%20had%20just%20met%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20marry%20me.%20I%20just%20smiled%20and%20rolled%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223894%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20getting%20married%20in%20Sicily%20on%20a%20sunny%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6813b4263fe8d3928364a829%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222921%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20eloped%2C%20and%20then%20married%20again%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20Sicily.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20credit%3A%20Becky%20Elizabeth%20Britton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22015ebc57-0b96-4d23-b717-8d940a7cfb67%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20saw%20marriage%20as%20an%20excuse%20for%20comp